cs.CL, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE 

The paper discusses techniques for automatically extracting relations between entities in text, which is a common task in natural language processing. This falls under the sub-category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). Additionally, the extracted relations can be used for information retrieval (cs.IR), and the paper discusses various machine learning techniques (cs.AI, cs.LG) for relation extraction. Finally, the paper also mentions recent trends in neural network-based approaches (cs.NE) for relation extraction.
